invalid type: string "htang Pass: Personal vehicles require permits, only available on alternate days.\n\nAccommodation\n-------------\nBudget: Guesthouses in Old Manali from ₹500-1500/night.\nMid-range: Hotels on Mall Road ₹2000-5000/night.\nLuxury: Span Resort, Solang Valley resorts ₹8000-20000/night.\nBook accommodation 2-3 months ahead for peak summer (May-June).", expected f64dar forest